&lt;li&gt;Define the technical roadmap for the London Sim Realism team, driving tight alignment with Waymo&#39;s overarching simulation and AI-first objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Direct the research and engineering of cutting-edge generative models for sensor-level and semantic-level simulation (Waymo World Model).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recruit, manage, and mentor a top-tier Sim Realism engineering organization, attracting elite talent in machine learning, generative AI, and simulation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with Real Estate &amp;amp; Workplace Services (REWS) to design and support a site strategy.&lt;/li&gt;
